locality: T1. Minziro Forest Reserve, Kinwa Kyaishemweru forest area SE of Minziro Village.
Tongwe East Forest, Isa riverine forest with Syzygium sp., Julbernardia sp., and Pterocarpus tinctorius.
Mbeya: Mbeya Distirct, Mporoto Ridge; ca 4 km NW of Igoma on NW slope of Mlima wa Bangi (Hemp Hill).
Falls in the Vina river, c. 15 km SE. of Ngaoundéré.
